Package: SafetyNarrativeGenerator
Title: Safety Narrative Generator for Clinical Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ginny", "Peng", , "pengvirginia@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny application for generating standardized safety narratives 
    from clinical trial data. Features include data import, customizable templates,
    batch processing, and interactive visualizations.
